scripts.name: Add to wishlist - nookazon.com
scripts.description: Allow to add multiple items to a whishlist at once. Go to wishlist, enter the items separated by coma in the search bar and click the import button. Format is itemName - variante. Ex: Avery - ungifted,stone,wood,Sasha. If no variante specified, all are added. Works on both PC and mobile (firefox). The sharing of script on nookazon discord is prohibited, so please keep this to yourself.
